OL,4,CBernie Madoff: Disgraced financier dies
OL,5,Cin prison
OL,6, Disgraced Wall Street financier Bernie
OL,7, Madoff, who was convicted for conning
OL,8, investors out of tens of billions of
OL,9, dollars, has died in prison at age 82.
OL,11,FThe death was announced by the US
OL,12,FBureau of Prisons.
OL,14,FMr Madoff had been serving a 150-year
OL,15,Fsentence after he admitted in 2009 that
OL,16,Fhe had defrauded investors through a
OL,17,FPonzi scheme, which paid out using
OL,18,Ftheir money rather than any profits.
OL,20,FIt collapsed during the financial
OL,21,Fcrisis of 2008.
